title: (x) Anna Nicole Smith font - Countryhouse {Stephen}
content:
I should know better than to admit needing this font, or one like it... but it's a must-have for a project i'm working on. I'm looking for the curly font used in this banner ad. If anybody knows what it is, I'd greatly appreciate it.
